        Configure blog type
      </h3>
    </div>
    
    <div class="modal-body">
      
      <form>
        
        <label>
          Blog type name
        </label>
        <input type="text" name="blogtypename" placeholder="Enter Blog Type Name" value="" class="fullwidth-input">
